node.text: WWE’s half-year award winners are revealed on @wwethebump as we celebrate the best of 2021 so far. Awards such as Superstar of the Half-Year, Match of the Half-Year, Rivalry of the Half-Year and much more are given out, including The Bumpies’ Lifetime Achievement Award for the one and only @dmcintyrewwe! Presented by @mgmresortsintl.

node.title: The 2021 Bumpy Awards: WWE’s The Bump, Aug. 4, 2021
